<div class="card hidden" id="page2">
    <h1>Thanks for choosing the only option ‚ù§Ô∏è</h1>
    <p>
        From now on, you‚Äôre officially in charge of maintaining my heart
        and keeping our love in perfect rhythm ‚Äî no system errors allowed.
        Let‚Äôs make this our favorite long-term project.
